<div class="container wow fadeInUp titulo">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h1 class="section-title">In development</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <% if notice %>
          <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if alert %>
          <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
        <% end %>  
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <img src="<%= image_path("Chloe.png") %>" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>Hi guys! We are developing our next game. It would be a platformer action game with lots of puzzles, skills, cool art and so much more.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>A long journey is upon us. This will be our longest and hardest game till now.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>The game will have a lot of exciting things and we hope to have the demo ready for january 2018. Hope you guys stay in touch.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>